My real name is Allen. I enjoy writing and proofreading, and am native English speaker. For historical perspective, I joined on 14 Jan 2012, during the [[w:Wikipedia:SOPA_initiative|SOPA discussion]], but really started editing on 18 Mar 2012. Because I enjoy writing and copyediting, and frequently indulge in Wikipedia reading sessions (which occasionally get out of hand), becoming a Wikipedian and Wikibookian was a natural step. As of 2014, I'm a high school student.

Interests: [[w:computer programming|programming]], [[w:cryptography|cryptography]], [[w:languages|languages]].

Wikipedia articles I've worked on:
